1. *Čekali* smo dugo da dođeš (We waited a long time for you to come).
2. *Čekali* smo da pogledamo film (We waited to watch the movie).
3. *Čeka* li ona da odeš (Is she waiting for you to leave).
4. *Čeka*š da se ona vrati (Are you waiting for her to come back).
5. *Čekamo* da čujemo odgovor (We are waiting to hear the answer).
6. *Čekala* sam da se sastanemo (I waited for us to meet).